<strong><span style='mso-bidi-font-style:italic'>Rafiq R&uuml;st&#601;mli:
&quot;M&#601;nim yetirm&#601;l&#601;rimi Murad Rzayev &ouml;z ad&#305;na
&ccedil;&#305;x&#305;r&quot;<o:p></o:p></span></strong></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:2.0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
