lang=AZ-LATIN style='color:black;mso-ansi-language:AZ-LATIN'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:2.0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;
margin-left:2.0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:35.45pt'><span
lang=AZ-LATIN style='color:black;mso-ansi-language:AZ-LATIN'>&quot;Ustad
s&#601;n&#601;tkar Rafiq R&uuml;st&#601;mli b&#601;&#351;&#601;ri musiqini
biz&#601; t&#601;rc&uuml;m&#601;siz anlatd&#305;&quot;. </span><span
style='color:black'>Bu fikir Fransan&#305;n Lion &#351;&#601;h&#601;rind&#601;
milli musiqimizi dinl&#601;y&#601;n bir frans&#305;z jurnalist&#601;
m&#601;xsusdur. <span class=GramE>R.R&uuml;st&#601;mli s&#601;n&#601;tin&#601;
v&#601; onun &quot;Qaraba&#287; b&uuml;lb&uuml;ll&#601;ri&quot; ansambl&#305;na
